HTTP GET
http://localhost:8080/greeting
RESPONSE
{"id":1,"content":"Hello, World!"}

HTTP GET
http://localhost:8080/greeting?name=User
RESPONSE
{"id":1,"content":"Hello, User!"}

Gradle:
run the application
gradlew bootRun

build the JAR file
gradlew build

Run executable jar
java -jar build/libs/simplerest-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar


Maven:
run the application
mvnw spring-boot:run

build the JAR file
mvnw clean package

Run executable jar
java -jar target/simplerest-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar